The virgin Suicides is such a good movie. The subject of course is a little grim but the way its filmed is so dreamy and beautiful. You get lost in this world for a little while and leaves you with questions but not in a bad way. Sophia Coppola has a way with films that gets me every time. American Beauty is also along the same lines except to me a little more  complex. The characters are a little more developed and you get everything by the end of the movie.
Bought this for the amazing American Beauty, was surprised by how deeply moving The Virgin Suicides was, in its bewildering, melancholy way. Great package!
Sophia hits a home run with her adaptation of the Virgin Suicides.  Breathtaking performances guided by a steady young hand!

American Beauty is a classic with great acting and music. Visually entertaining as well. The Virgin Suicides is a great story with the same- great acting, music. Love them both, so it was fantastic to find them together.

This movie is one of my favorite all-time movies and won the Academy Award for Best Picture for 1999 and Kevin Spacey for Best Actor.  It also won three other Academy Awards. Although it deals with some very controversial subject matter and may be reserved for more mature audiences it really hits a home run in the way it brings you into the lives of a very dysfunctional family and world.  Although not for everyone, I highly recommend it if you like to see movies that take on controversial subjects and are not afraid to play them out on the screen.  The cast is exceptional, especially the performance of Kevin Spacey.
Its a great combo. Very happy with my purchase. I didn't even know the 2 movies came together and the price was unbeatable!
